title: Mr Boukadoum holds talks with Libyan counterpart
text: In anticipation Algeriaâ€™s chairmanship in the Peace and Security Council of the African Union, Minister of Foreign Affairs, Mr Sabri Boukadoum, held on Friday April 30th, 2021, talks with Libyan Minister of Foreign Affairs and International Cooperation, Mrs Nadjla El Mangoush, on the ways likely to reinforce our efforts in fostering the peace and reconciliation process in Libya.
